      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how none of this actually matters. like, in a billion years, the sun is gonna swallow everything and there wont even be a memory that we ever existed. it feels kind of stupid to keep trying so hard when the end result is just... nothing. absolute zero.",
